  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Host",
  "description": "<p><strong>Restaurant Host</strong></p><p>Take home at least $2,500 + $300 to $2,900 + $300 monthly (Included fixed incentive)<br /></p><p><strong>Who are we?</strong></p><p>Super Loco Group is Singapore’s leading Mexican restaurant group, and we are looking for a temporary, experienced Mobilisation Support to join the team. If you want to be part of a fantastic, growing brand, we would love to hear from you!<br /></p><p><strong>Who are you?</strong></p><p>You’re an energetic, outgoing team player, with good communication skills, a willingness to learn and a passion for restaurants.<br /></p><p><strong>What will you be doing?</strong></p><p>You will work alongside an energetic team to charm, surprise and delight our customers, and give them a memorable experience in our restaurants.<br /></p><ul><li><p>Greet every guest with big energy and warm Mexican hospitality! You’re the first smile they see!</p></li><li><p>Manage reservations and walk-ins, keep the vibes flowing, and make sure every guest gets the best seat for their experience.</p></li><li><p>Own the guest journey from the door to the table! Share menu highlights, answer questions, and help set the tone for a great night.</p></li><li><p>Run the waitlist like a pro: give friendly, honest wait times and keep guests excited while they wait.</p></li></ul><p><strong>What will you get?</strong></p><ul><li><p>A competitive monthly salary</p></li><li><p>Additional performance incentives up to $250</p></li><li><p>Comprehensive medical and dental insurance</p></li><li><p>Paid annual leave and Birthday leave</p></li><li><p>Staff meal and transport</p></li><li><p>The opportunity to develop and grow with the company</p></li></ul><p><strong>What’s next?</strong></p><ul><li><p>We will contact you to arrange a quick chat over the phone.</p></li><li><p>If it goes well, we’ll introduce you to your line manager, and if you hit it off you’ve got the gig!</p></li></ul>",
